---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="OpenClaw Memory Stack">
  <style>
    /* ── Nav ── */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      background: rgba(6, 8, 12, 0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .nav-logo span { color: var(--muted); }
    .nav-claw-icon { vertical-align: -4px; margin-right: 4px; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 500; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--fg-bright); text-shadow: none; }
    .nav-toggle { display: none; background: none; border: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 0.25rem; color: var(--muted); }
    .nav-toggle:hover { color: var(--fg-bright); }
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .nav-toggle { display: block; }
      .nav-links {
        display: none;
        position: absolute;
        top: 100%;
        left: 0; right: 0;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0;
        background: rgb(6, 8, 12);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
        padding: 0.5rem 0;
      }
      .nav-links.open { display: flex; }
      .nav-links a {
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        width: 100%;
      }
      .nav-links a:hover { background: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.05); }
    }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 10rem 2rem 5rem;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
    }
    .hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%; left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -60%);
      width: 600px; height: 600px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent-dim) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: -1;
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      background: var(--accent-dim);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-bright);
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.35rem 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .badge::before { content: '//'; color: var(--muted); }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      color: var(--fg-bright);
    }
    .hero h1 .glow {
      color: var(--accent);
      text-shadow: 0 0 40px var(--accent-glow);
    }
    .hero .subtitle {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 560px;
      margin: 0 auto 3rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .hero-cta {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: var(--bg);
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: 0.85rem 2.2rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all 0.25s;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-family: var(--font-sans);
    }
    .hero-cta:hover {
      background: var(--accent-hover);
      color: var(--bg);
      text-shadow: none;
      box-shadow: 0 0 30px var(--accent-glow);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
    .hero-price {
      display: block;
      margin-top: 1rem;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    /* ── Terminal demo ── */
    .terminal-wrap {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto 6rem;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }
    .terminal {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-bright);
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), 0 0 40px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.05);
    }
    .terminal-bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      background: var(--surface-elevated);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .terminal-dot {
      width: 10px; height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--border-bright);
    }
    .terminal-dot:nth-child(1) { background: #ff5f57; }
    .terminal-dot:nth-child(2) { background: #ffbd2e; }
    .terminal-dot:nth-child(3) { background: #28c840; }
    .terminal-title {
      flex: 1;
      text-align: center;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-right: 40px;
    }
    .terminal-body {
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .terminal-body .prompt { color: var(--accent); }
    .terminal-body .cmd { color: var(--fg-bright); }
    .terminal-body .comment { color: var(--muted); font-style: italic; }
    .terminal-body .output { color: var(--muted); }
    .terminal-body .success { color: var(--green); }

    /* ── Section titles ── */
    .section {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
    }
    .section-label {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    .section h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--fg-bright);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }
    .section .section-desc {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 500px;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    /* ── Feature cards ── */
    .features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .feature-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.75rem;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }
    .feature-card:hover {
      border-color: var(--border-bright);
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.05);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 36px; height: 36px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      background: var(--accent-dim);
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .feature-card h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--fg-bright);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
    }
    .feature-card p {
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    /* ── Routing flow ── */
    .routing-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }
    .route-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      overflow: hidden;
      word-break: break-word;
    }
    .route-label {
      color: var(--fg-bright);
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
    }
    .route-arrow {
      color: var(--accent);
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .route-target {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    /* ── Compare stats ── */
    .compare-header-cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .compare-stat {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 10px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .compare-stat-number {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--accent);
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .compare-stat-label {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--fg-bright);
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .compare-stat-label span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
    }

    /* ── Compare table ── */
    .compare-table-wrap {
      overflow-x: auto;
      margin: 0 -0.5rem;
    }
    .compare-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
    .compare-table th {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-align: left;
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border-bright);
    }
    .compare-table th:not(:first-child) {
      text-align: center;
      width: 35%;
    }
    .compare-table td {
      padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      color: var(--fg);
      vertical-align: top;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .compare-table td:not(:first-child) {
      text-align: left;
    }
    .compare-table td:first-child {
      font-weight: 500;
      color: var(--fg-bright);
      width: 30%;
    }
    .compare-table tr:hover {
      background: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.03);
    }
    .compare-table td.yes {
      color: #28c840;
    }
    .compare-table td.no {
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    .compare-table td.partial {
      color: #ffbd2e;
    }
    .compare-group td {
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      font-size: 0.7rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      color: var(--accent);
      padding: 1.5rem 1rem 0.5rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-bright);
      font-weight: 700;
    }


    /* ── CTA ── */
    .cta-section {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
    }
    .cta-box {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border-bright);
      border-radius: 16px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .cta-box::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top, var(--accent-dim) 0%, transparent 60%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .cta-box .price {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--fg-bright);
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      position: relative;
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
    }
    .cta-box .price-note {
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    .cta-box .cta-btn-wrap { position: relative; }

    /* ── Disclaimers ── */
    .disclaimers-section {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 2rem 2rem 4rem;
    }
    .disclaimers {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 0.75rem;
      list-style: none;
    }
    .disclaimers li {
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 6px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
    .disclaimers li strong {
      color: var(--fg);
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    /* ── FAQ ── */
    .faq-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }
    .faq-item {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .faq-item[open] {
      border-color: var(--border-bright);
    }
    .faq-item summary {
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--fg-bright);
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }
    .faq-item summary::after {
      content: '+';
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
      color: var(--accent);
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      transition: transform 0.2s;
    }
    .faq-item[open] summary::after {
      transform: rotate(45deg);
    }
    .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
    .faq-item p {
      padding: 0 1.25rem 1rem;
      font-size: 0.88rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }
    .faq-item strong {
      color: var(--fg);
    }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 3rem 2rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-family: var(--font-mono);
    }
    footer .links { display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; justify-content: center; margin-top: 0.75rem; }
    footer .links a { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.75rem; }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .compare-header-cards {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    /* ── Responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      nav { padding: 0.75rem 1rem; }
      .hero { padding: 8rem 1.25rem 3rem; }
      .section { padding: 3rem 1.25rem; }
      .terminal-wrap { padding: 0 1.25rem; }
      .cta-section { padding: 3rem 1.25rem; }
    }
  </style>

  <nav>
    <div class="nav-logo">
      <svg class="nav-claw-icon" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 120 120" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <defs><linearGradient id="lg" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#ff4d4d"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#991b1b"/></linearGradient></defs>
        <path d="M60 10 C30 10 15 35 15 55 C15 75 30 95 45 100 L45 110 L55 110 L55 100 C55 100 60 102 65 100 L65 110 L75 110 L75 100 C90 95 105 75 105 55 C105 35 90 10 60 10Z" fill="url(#lg)"/>
        <path d="M20 45 C5 40 0 50 5 60 C10 70 20 65 25 55 C28 48 25 45 20 45Z" fill="url(#lg)"/>
        <path d="M100 45 C115 40 120 50 115 60 C110 70 100 65 95 55 C92 48 95 45 100 45Z" fill="url(#lg)"/>
        <path d="M45 15 Q35 5 30 8" stroke="#ff4d4d" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <path d="M75 15 Q85 5 90 8" stroke="#ff4d4d" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round"/>
        <circle cx="45" cy="35" r="6" fill="#050810"/><circle cx="75" cy="35" r="6" fill="#050810"/>
        <circle cx="46" cy="34" r="2.5" fill="#00e5cc"/><circle cx="76" cy="34" r="2.5" fill="#00e5cc"/>
      </svg>
      openclaw<span>/memory-stack</span>
    </div>
    <button class="nav-toggle" id="nav-toggle" aria-label="Menu">
      <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><line x1="3" y1="6" x2="21" y2="6"/><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/><line x1="3" y1="18" x2="21" y2="18"/></svg>
    </button>
    <div class="nav-links" id="nav-links">
      <a href="#features">Features</a>
      <a href="#compare">vs Native</a>
      <a href="#faq">FAQ</a>
      <a href="/manage">Manage License</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="badge">v0.1.3 — Official OpenClaw Plugin</div>
    <h1>Total recall.<br/><span class="glow">90% fewer tokens.</span></h1>
    <p class="subtitle">
      Your agent forgets past decisions and burns tokens re-reading the same context.
      Memory Stack runs 5 search engines locally, returns only what matters, and never loses a fact.
      Bring your own API key to unlock LLM-powered fact extraction for the complete experience.
    </p>
    <button class="hero-cta" id="buy-btn">
      Get Memory Stack
      <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="none"><path d="M3 8h10M9 4l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
    </button>
    <span class="hero-price">$49 &mdash; one-time purchase, no subscription</span>
  </div>

  <div class="terminal-wrap">
    <div class="terminal">
      <div class="terminal-bar">
        <div class="terminal-dot"></div>
        <div class="terminal-dot"></div>
        <div class="terminal-dot"></div>
        <div class="terminal-title">openclaw-memory</div>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-body">
        <div><span class="comment"># Install — one command, done</span></div>
        <div><span class="prompt">$</span> <span class="cmd">./install.sh --key=oc-starter-xxxxxxxxxxxx</span></div>
        <div><span class="success">  [OK]  License verified</span></div>
        <div><span class="success">  [OK]  Registered as OpenClaw memory plugin</span></div>
        <div>&nbsp;</div>
        <div><span class="comment"># Restart OpenClaw — memory is now active</span></div>
        <div><span class="prompt">$</span> <span class="cmd">openclaw gateway restart</span></div>
        <div><span class="success">  [OK]  Memory Stack v2 registered (engines: fts5+qmd+memorymd+rescue+lossless)</span></div>
        <div>&nbsp;</div>
        <div><span class="comment"># Just talk — memory works in the background</span></div>
        <div><span class="output">  You: What did we decide about the API design?</span></div>
        <div><span class="success">  [memory] 5 engines searched → RRF fusion → L0 tier (~98 tokens)</span></div>
        <div><span class="output">  Agent: We decided to use REST with /api/v2/...</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section" id="features">
    <div class="section-label">// why memory stack</div>
    <h2>Less tokens. More memory. Faster answers.</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">Every wasted token is money burned. Memory Stack eliminates the waste.</p>
    <div class="features">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F4A1;</div>
        <h3>3-Tier Token Control</h3>
        <p>Native memory dumps full text every time. Memory Stack gives you three tiers: L0 auto-recall at ~100 tokens, L1 summaries at ~800, L2 full content on demand. 90% fewer tokens per search — your agent gets exactly what it needs, nothing more.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F50D;</div>
        <h3>5-Engine Rank Fusion</h3>
        <p>One search fires 5 engines in parallel — FTS5, QMD semantic search, markdown, rescue database, and lossless DAG. Results merge via Reciprocal Rank Fusion + MMR diversity reranking. Right answer on the first try. No wasted tokens chasing wrong context.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F6E1;</div>
        <h3>Never Forget a Decision</h3>
        <p>When conversations get long, compression eats old messages. Memory Stack extracts key facts — decisions, deadlines, requirements — into a dedicated SQLite store before they disappear. Your agent recalls them instantly instead of you re-explaining. Zero wasted tokens.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F517;</div>
        <h3>Knowledge Graph</h3>
        <p>Flat text search forces your agent to re-read everything to find connections. Memory Stack builds a local knowledge graph — multi-hop BFS, evolution chains, PageRank, community detection. "What depends on X?" answered in one hop, not ten re-reads.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x1F9F9;</div>
        <h3>Self-Cleaning Memory</h3>
        <p>Duplicates and junk cost real money every time your agent reads them. 4-level deduplication (exact, normalized, substring, cosine) runs automatically. Health score 0-100 shows exactly what's wasting tokens. Your memory stays lean, your bill stays flat.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#x26A1;</div>
        <h3>Bring Your Key. Unlock Full Power.</h3>
        <p>Core search runs offline out of the box. Add any LLM API key — OpenAI, Anthropic, Ollama, MLX, or any OpenAI-compatible endpoint — and Memory Stack auto-detects it. LLM-powered fact extraction kicks in: every conversation produces structured decisions, deadlines, and entities stored permanently. A few cents per session saves dollars of wasted tokens. Your key, your choice of provider.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section" id="how">
    <div class="section-label">// how it works</div>
    <h2>Install once. Every conversation gets cheaper.</h2>
    <p class="section-desc">One command installs it as OpenClaw's memory provider. Token savings start immediately.</p>
    <div class="routing-grid">
      <div class="route-item">
        <div>
          <div class="route-label">You talk to OpenClaw</div>
          <div class="route-arrow">&rarr; <span class="route-target">auto-recall kicks in</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="route-item">
        <div>
          <div class="route-label">Relevant memories found</div>
          <div class="route-arrow">&rarr; <span class="route-target">injected before response</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="route-item">
        <div>
          <div class="route-label">Agent responds</div>
          <div class="route-arrow">&rarr; <span class="route-target">key facts saved to rescue</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="route-item">
        <div>
          <div class="route-label">Conversation gets long</div>
          <div class="route-arrow">&rarr; <span class="route-target">compaction happens</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="route-item">
        <div>
          <div class="route-label">You ask about old decisions</div>
          <div class="route-arrow">&rarr; <span class="route-target">rescue store has them</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section" id="compare">
